    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "一、主函数：TurnSignalIndications_Run(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：SWC 主状态机，每个周期运行一次。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "执行顺序 ："
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "检查 GetPermitExecution() & SUSD_HWREADY_ECUNORESET 。",
        "检查 GetP_TURN_SIGNAL_INDICATOR_ENABLED() 。",
        "处理 2605 no-action 节拍（ g_noaction2605counter ）。",
        "处理左转延时定时器：到时后更新左图标、更新左声效状态、停表。",
        "调 evaluateLeftTurnChimeStatus() 处理左 chime 请求。",
        "处理右转延时定时器：到时后更新右图标、更新右声效状态、停表。",
        "再次调用 evaluateLeftTurnChimeStatus() （右侧复用左侧函数）。",
        "处理左右 ParkLight I/O 定时器到时逻辑。",
        "CheckTimeouts() 做 fail-soft/补偿更新。",
        "HazardActivationCondition() 更新 OFF 模式双闪激活逻辑。",
        "UpdateReminderStatus() 更新 reminder 状态。",
        "根据 IsReminderActive() 输出 PutTurnSignalWarningOn(1/0) 。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "左/右逻辑是镜像结构，唯一区别为右侧部分 Hazard 被注释"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Interface/image-2026-3-16_16-40-55.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Interface/image-2026-3-16_16-40-55.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "二、对外接口"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "以下函数来自 LHT_ControlTurnSignalIndication.c ，由 RTE 事件/调度调用。"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. RtTrnLmpAtv_Clbk(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：右转灯激活回调"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "若 P_TURN_SIGNAL_INDICATOR_ENABLED 关闭，直接返回。",
        "调用 HazardOffModeTimer() 更新 OFF 模式双闪计时状态。",
        "若右转定时器未运行，则启动 g_RtTurn_SigTimer 。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "把“右转灯输入变化”转换为“延迟后处理”（防抖/同步车辆灯和仪表图标）。"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. LftTrnLmpAtv_Clbk(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：左转灯激活回调。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "与右侧完全对称，操作 g_LftTurn_SigTimer 。"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. PrkLtRightIO_Clbk(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：右侧 Park Light 输入回调。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "逻 使能后启动 g_RTIOTurn_SigTimer ，用于延时触发右侧指示更新。"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4. PrkLtLeftIO_Cblk(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：左侧 Park Light 输入回调。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "使能后启动 g_LftIOTurn_SigTimer 。"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "5. HazSwAtv_Clbk(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：Hazard 开关回调。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "若任一 Park Light 输入为真，则立即调用左右 IndicatorTurnSignal*_Delayed() 更新显示。这不是完整双闪策略入口，完整策略仍在 TurnSignalIndications_Run() 中周期执行。"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "6. TrnSwAct_Clbk(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：转向拨杆状态变化回调。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "核心逻辑 ："
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "检测拨杆状态变化（与 g_u8PrevTrnSwAct 比较）。",
        "变化后先将 reminder 置 OFF。",
        "若拨杆进入 LEFT/RIGHT："
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "记住“转向开始时里程”，后续在 RUN 周期中判断是否超出提醒距离。"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "7. IndicatorTurnSignalLeft_Delayed(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：左侧转向提示（图标）延迟更新。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "判定条件（电源模式 RUN/ACC/OFF 下） ："
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "左转灯信号可用且状态为 ON_WITH_TELLTALE；或",
        "左 ParkLight 可用且 ON，且 Hazard 信号可用并且 Hazard=OFF。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "满足则 TurnSignalIndicator(LEFT, ON) ，否则 TurnSignalIndicator(LEFT, OFF) 。"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "8. IndicatorTurnSignalRight_Delayed(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：右侧转向提示延迟更新。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "与左侧类似，使用右侧输入。"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "9. TurnSignalIndications_Init(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：初始化。"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "重置 reminder/sound/power/hazard 历史状态及相关计时变量。",
        "获取唤醒源：若不是 SUSD_WKSOURCE_CAN5_CLUSTER ，清零 g_u32OdoAtTurnSwitchAct 。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "特定唤醒源下保留里程"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 2,
      "text": "三、内部函数（Static）"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "1. TurnSignalIndicator(uint8 u8Position, uint8 u8OnOff)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：统一输出左右图标。"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "左： PutIndLft(1/0) + HMIUpdateIndication_Client(FU_CLUSTERHUD,1,...) + HMIUpdateIndication_Client(FU_BSP_Indicator,1,...)",
        "右： PutIndRght(1/0) + ...index=2..."
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "2. IsReminderActive(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ： g_u8ReminderStatus == CeOCD_TurnInd_REMINDER_ACTIVE 返回 1。"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "3. UpdateReminderStatus(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：距离提醒状态机。"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "PowerMode=RUN",
        "TurnSwitchActivation_Available",
        "Hazard_Available 且 Hazard=OFF",
        "拨杆为 LEFT 或 RIGHT"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "以上条件满足时："
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "u32OdoNow = GetVehicleOdometer()",
        "若 u32OdoNow - g_u32OdoAtTurnSwitchAct > P_CHIME_TURN_DISTANCE -> ACTIVE"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "否则 reminder OFF。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "排查 reminder 问题时，优先确认是否真的经历了 OFF -> CALCULATING -> ACTIVE`这条路径。"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Interface/image-2026-3-17_16-31-18.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Interface/image-2026-3-17_16-31-18.png"
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "4. GetSound(uint8 u8OnOff)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：根据 On/Off + reminder 状态选择 chime ID。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "映射："
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "ON + reminder active -> P_GB_CHIME_ID_2605_ENABLE",
        "ON + reminder inactive -> P_GB_CHIME_ID_2660_ENABLE",
        "OFF + reminder active -> CeOCD_TurnInd_SOUND_NONE",
        "OFF + reminder inactive -> P_GB_CHIME_ID_2665_ENABLE"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "5. CheckTimeouts(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：超时/可用性补偿（fail-soft）。"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": false,
      "items": [
        "若左右灯或 ParkLight 可用，触发对应延迟函数。",
        "若处于 CRANK、Hazard 可用、或刚从 CRANK 离开，也强制更新左右图标。",
        "最后更新 g_PowerMode_Prev 。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "level": 3,
      "text": "6. HazardActivationCondition(void)"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "功能 ：判断 OFF 电源模式下何时重启 Hazard Off timer。"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "触发重启计时的典型条件："
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "ordered": true,
      "items": [
        "Hazard=TRUE + 当前 OFF，且旧电源模式来自 ACC/RUN/CRANK。",
        "当前 OFF + Hazard 从 FALSE 边沿到 TRUE。",
        "当前 OFF + Hazard=TRUE + DriverDoorAjar 从 FALSE 边沿到 TRUE。"
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "每次触发都会 Timer_Stop 再 Timer_Start g_u32HazardOffModeTimer"
    },
    {
      "type": "image",
      "src": "https://inside-docupedia.bosch.com/confluence/download/attachments/embedded-page/CARSFW/Interface/image-2026-3-17_16-49-16.png?api=v2",
      "alt": "",
      "local_path": "_images/Interface/image-2026-3-17_16-49-16.png"
    }
  ],
